2003-08-18 13:56 UTC+0200 Przemyslaw Czerpak <druzus@polbox.com>
  * xharbour/xharbour.spec
    * minor corecrections

  * xharbour/contrib/libct/Makefile
  * xharbour/contrib/libct/makefile.bc
  * xharbour/contrib/libct/makefile.vc
